                  "body": {
                    "type": "TextualBody",
                    "value": "<p>gogue when he ascends the pulpit. Be-<lb/>sides, he has been reelected only for\n                one<lb/> year. Oh! He is a man of principle<lb/> &amp; character. Counsel your correspondent<lb/>\n                <persName><sic>counsellor</sic></persName> to be more candid &amp; truth-<lb/>ful in\n                future.</p>\n            <p rend=\"indent(1)\">Why have you not a word of<lb/> censure for the attempted vandalism\n                of <persName>Dr<lb/> Sachs</persName> of <placeName>Berlin</placeName>? To me, that\n                man is<lb/> henceforth more hateful &amp; obnoxious than<lb/> even\n                    <persName>Cardinal Antonelli</persName>. Why have<lb/> you not yet said a word\n                about the<lb/> fanatic acts of the Orthodox of\n                    <placeName>Amster-<lb/>dam</placeName>. Yet, you scold, because “rich\n                Re-<lb/>formers” will not suffer themselves to be<lb/> brow-beaten into hypocrisy by\n                ortho-<lb/>dox fanatics &amp; hypocrites. I am open<lb/> with you: I sometimes get\n                perplexed<lb/> in my respect for the <hi rend=\"underline\">Orthodox</hi>;<lb/> for\n                withholding truth borders very<lb/> closely upon uttering untruth!”</p>\n            <p>I was not present at the Banquet;<lb/> but I <hi rend=\"underline\">know</hi> that the\n                “rich reformers” re-</p>"
